Template: flexplorer/FLEXIBEE_URL
Type: string
_Default: https://demo.flexibee.eu
_Description: FlexiBee API URL:
 URL with protocol, hostname and optional port ( https://localhost:5434 )

Template: flexplorer/FLEXIBEE_LOGIN
Type: string
_Default: winstrom
_Description: FlexiBee API Username:
 User with prermisson to use REST API

Template: flexplorer/FLEXIBEE_PASSWORD
Type: string
_Default: winstrom
_Description: FlexiBee API password:
 Password for user with prermisson to use REST API

Template: flexplorer/FLEXIBEE_COMPANY
Type: string
_Default: demo
_Description: Selected company:
 First company opened by default


Template: flexibudget/DATABASE_TYPE
Type: select
Choices: mysql, postgresql, sqlite
_Default: mysql
_Description: Type of used database:
 You can use databases supported by PHP PDO

Template: flexibudget/DATABASE_HOST
Type: string
_Default: localhost
_Description: Where get database:
 Use local database in most cases

Template: flexibudget/DATABASE_PORT
Type: string
_Default: 3306
_Description: database port:
 3306 for MySQL, 5435 for PostgreSQL

Template: flexibudget/DATABASE_USER
Type: string
_Default: flexibudget
_Description: Database user name:
 may bee default in most cases

Template: flexibudget/DATABASE_PASSWORD
Type: string
_Default: flexibudget
_Description: Database password we use:
 Please use save pasword in production enviroment

Template: flexibudget/DATABASE_NAME
Type: string
_Default: flexibudget
_Description: Database schema name:
 may bee default in most cases
